<note id="fs-id1167660185790" class="microbiology link-to-learning">

<para id="fs-id1167662488566">Because prion-contaminated materials are potential sources of infection for clinical scientists and physicians, both the <link url="https://www.openstax.org/l/22WHOprion">World Health Organization</link> and <link url="https://www.openstax.org/l/22CDCprion">CDC</link> provide information to inform, educate and minimize the risk of infections due to prions.</para>
</note>
